'''Nataša Tučev''' ([[17 March]], [[1968]]) is an assistant in the English department of the [[wikipedia:University of Niš|University of Niš]]. Her work primarily focuses on the works of [[wikipedia:Seamus Heaney|Heaney]], [[wikipedia:W. B. Yeats|Yeats]] and [[wikipedia:John Millington Synge|Synge]].
